{"tid":784562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓槍擊案　兩名支那公民死亡","createTime":"2018-08-18T13:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T16:07:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bc00ad89b601977541c88ff7bff6fe6bbf1f82","tid":784562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1413185_1_L_20180818190335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1413185_1_L_20180818190335.jpg&h=7c264da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓馬尼拉發生槍擊案，兩名中國公民死亡，另外兩人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地中午前，馬尼拉警方表示，兩名槍手駕駛電單車，在馬尼拉市中心大街上開槍，30歲事主當場死亡，另一名35歲事主送院後不治，另外兩人受傷，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，未知槍手動機，正調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐菲律賓使館表示注意到有關報道，正核實情況和死者身分。"},{"pid":"3137ff2cb89e6debe7edc33ebc596dda7bb775a4","tid":784562,"uid":2419,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"狗都唔去菲律賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148b13088f121f183e72223bfa875879b9bf841f","tid":784562,"uid":38216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"088fa68b720996b04cc8f9be8f4ce39d169edeae","tid":784562,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20101006/large/06la5p5ru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20101006%2Flarge%2F06la5p5ru.jpg&h=a53294e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靠呢班特警, 真係日日發生槍擊案唔出奇"},{"pid":"c62ed886da1b9b3774c31dc4fc8568253fc1a5cb","tid":784562,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"懇請習大大出兵菲律賓，還死者公道"},{"pid":"7687c37a046be33bfbc26a3b6bb8f0bdbfde4288","tid":784562,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB